Keep your nose out of mafia business, or he might put a hit on you. Been a while since he gave me a challenging target.
Actually, Go ahead, Piss him off! Then I'll have a reason to hunt you!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Greetings Citizen. Anything i can help you with?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Actually no, but how is an officer down here not getting deleted on sight?

property.name: Text 1
property.value: I have built some trust with the locals. Let's leave it at that. Have a good day!

property.name: Text 1
property.value: Oh good, you arrived! And i see the badge to boot! I'm preparing something to deal with this mafia issue, and i think you might be just the navi to help me. I will organize my materials and get back to you about it.
